---
title: Roast Root Veggies & Quinoa with Spiced Nuts
description: We toyed with calling this delish little salad ‘Fruits of the Forest’ because we’re whimsical and a little bit ridiculous if we’re being honest. But come on! This winning combo of nuts, seeds, feta and root veg will have you feeling a bit Disney-princess-with-a-forest-animal-sidekick too.
